{"tid":1763832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好屌香港人開始收貨","createTime":"2019-11-30T15:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T07:09:22.000Z","uid":209932,"like":69,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"97265dbc6a225dd0eaae47bd74549d212fc7c61d","tid":1763832,"uid":209932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:52:18.000Z","msg":"戴返頭盔先 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n雖然still far from victory <br />\n但係呢場運動走到宜家 大家都出左好多力<br />\n其實已經好勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可能好介意所謂俾啲掌聲自己咁既打飛機行為<br />\n不過要換位諗返對好多香港人 <br />\n呢次係第一次參與政治 第一次抗爭咁多個月 第一次食tg 第一次投票<br />\n係會辛苦會攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會想就咁收貨<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">簡單啲講 就係雖然大家係同路人 但係大家係心態上唔一定一致 尤其過左咁耐 會有人脫隊係正常</span></ins></strong><br />\n如果呢個時候屌佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同屌票一樣 是on9的 只會令人卻步<br />\n需要嘅係令大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重拾熱誠嘅行為同話語</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n具體嚟講 我覺得宜家需要嘅係對香港人負擔較輕 具凝聚力嘅 例如之前 和你唱 和你shop 人鏈 重建連儂牆之類嘅活動 負擔較少得嚟 又可以比香港人再集結<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夢想當然係keep到抗爭力度 又keep到團體意識 但係手足犠牲換嚟嘅激情開始退燒 要堅持落去 就要考慮民意問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後貼返張<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">自己出嘅</span>文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgoVAZK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgoVAZK.jpg&h=cb1a6c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgCvpS8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgCvpS8.png&h=72f900f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6505f0acfb57eaf2e3a66128c82a033b9ab14f5","tid":1763832,"uid":209932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b90d8f941c7ae7ec3248a1cf7ff83b37ab78d87","tid":1763832,"uid":286735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ce950140d8930e1b735d87d07f43d1583c8de77","tid":1763832,"uid":209932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:55:33.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"e6ab143814708795b3855404248203fd59419ac5","tid":1763832,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"eb2bbce43dad9603ad8fcc23deab1a63a9c24cc5","tid":1763832,"uid":209932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"5af390a3dcb76a6892b9e5f8978cda6024a5f6ed","tid":1763832,"uid":181025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"講得好！ 正面d! <br />\n一齊行落去！！！"},{"pid":"361f436f0dbedf6e7126a2b2740b78921da058ab","tid":1763832,"uid":293802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:01:50.000Z","msg":"推.<br />\n<br />\n不過我只係唔想大家又因為手足死 或 受傷 先再催化大家上街示威<br />\n<br />\n聽日尖咀見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22de4fc3bc8b56fe30c58d1a73ba458f9a7beb90","tid":1763832,"uid":81507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"好多人無咩記性<br />\n721 831 101 個d要成日提住"},{"pid":"317d6a7bade57f5958996671ce8fe560facfb249","tid":1763832,"uid":209932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3370cca31340ad975f20a614d7570ff90076bcdb","tid":1763832,"uid":209932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"502147912813983b0d09c7ff5d38bbe269d9d3c0","tid":1763832,"uid":209932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:15:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7eb8110bf1dc39a34e4cb80499ad21e0e6eac032","tid":1763832,"uid":209932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim